      <lg xml:id="TolE0124">
<l>āṉiṉ ṉakaramu mataṉō raṟṟē</l>
<l>nāṇmuṉ varūum vaṉmutaṟ ṟoḻiṟkē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The <foreign xml:lang="ta">ṉ</foreign> of <foreign xml:lang="ta">āṉ</foreign> is changed identically when it comes</l>
<l>between [a noun denoting] lunar constellation<note
              place="foot"><foreign xml:lang="ta">nāḷ.</foreign> Iḷamp. quotes <foreign xml:lang="ta">paraṇiyār koṇṭāṉ</foreign> as illustration : <foreign xml:lang="ta">paraṇi</foreign> ' the second lunar asterism '.</note></l>
<l>and a verb beginning with plosive.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
